summary: SummaryLancôme Rénergie H.P.N. 300-Peptide Cream: An anti-aging cream with over 300 different types of Peptides, that reduces the appearance of lower face sagging, wrinkles, & dark spots.
details: DetailsBenefitsRénergie H.P.N. 300-Peptide Cream combines 3 ingredients represented by the name H.P.N. (Hyaluronic Acid, over 300 different Peptides, and Niacinamide) into a highly sensorial formula to reach an exceptional level of efficacy.Peptides are well known for their key role in skin renewal and are among skin's best ally against visible signs of aging.An unprecedented number and variety of peptides have been formulated into this unique cream: the complementary effect of the 300 peptides stimulates faster and enhanced skin renewal.This innovative formula helps improve visible signs of aging, such as: wrinkles, dark spots, & lower face sagging, with clinically significant results as early as two weeks.Committed to Science & Sustainability: This unique combination of peptides in Lancôme's formula is obtained from the protein extracts of three naturally derived sources, using green sciences.Key IngredientsHyaluronic Acid: Ferment-based and obtained using biotechnology, hyaluronic acid is known to absorb several times its own weight in water, helping to smooth and re-plump the skin. Lancôme's Hyaluronic acid offers enhanced skin penetration and additional benefits on wrinkles and skin roughness.300 types of Peptides: Ultra-concentrated and potent, this combination of more than 300 types of natural peptides helps the skin appear renewed by improving firmness, elasticity, and wrinkles.Niacinamide (or vitamin B3): Known to soothe the skin, contribute to skin tone management and help visibly reduce dark spots.*Ingredient benefits are based on product formula testing, not on the individual ingredients.Research ResultsClinically Significant Results:Decreased appearance of wrinkles -21% and fine lines -26%*Reduced visibility of dark spots -22%*Skin tone is more even +22%*Improved firmness +38%*Lower face sagging reduced -27%*Consumer Self Assessment Results:96% agree overall skin appearance looks improved**93% agree skin looks regenerated/renewed**86% agree skin appears younger***Based on self-assessment results in an 8-week consumer study with 58 women**Based on 8-week results in a clinical study of 45 womenItem 2621289How To UseFor best results, use this day moisturizer consistently as a part of your morning routine. Apply once a day on the face, neck, and décolleté after cleansing, toning, and using your facial serums. Gently massage into skin using small, upward, circular motions until the cream is fully absorbed.IngredientsAqua / Water, Glycerin, Dimethicone, Cetearyl Alcohol, Theobroma Grandiflorum Seed Butter, Alcohol Denat., Cetearyl Isononanoate, Niacinamide, Glyceryl Stearate, PEG-100 Stearate, Isopropyl Palmitate, Octyldodecanol, Cyclodextrin, Hydrolyzed Lupine Protein, Pisum Sativum Extract / Pea Extract, Adenosine, Capryloyl Salicylic Acid, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Hydrolyzed Linseed Extract, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-Di-T-Butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Trisodium Ethylenediamine Disuccinate, Tocopheryl Acetate, Cera Alba / Beeswax, Orbignya Oleifera Seed Oil, Simmondsia Chinensis Butter / Jojoba Butter, Cetearyl Glucoside, Citric Acid, Hydroxyethyl Acrylate/Sodium Acryloyldimethyl Taurate Copolymer, Polysorbate 60, Potassium Cetyl Phosphate, Sorbitan Isostearate, Tocopherol, Dimethicone/Polyglycerin-3 Crosspolymer, Benzyl Alcohol, Geraniol, Limonene, Chlorphenesin, Dipropylene Glycol, Phenoxyethanol, Sodium Benzoate, Perfume / Fragrance.Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details

reviews.headline: So nice
reviews.comments: I just purchased my second jar of this cream.  I like it very much but do not see what it actually did for my skin.  Unfortunately I have a weakness for buying products when they are on sale and this was 50 percent off.  After I am finished with this jar I think I am going to try Loreal Paris products and see if there really is a difference or am I paying for the name and packaging.  All in all I like the texture of the cream goes on wonderfully and does make my face soft.

reviews.headline: Lancome
reviews.comments: Love this product and the trip made better when the rep was present. Love her

reviews.headline: Be careful!  This cream comes SPF and no SPF
reviews.comments: I am a long time customer of this product, but didn't realize the product name and packaging is almost identical for the TWO DIFFERENT moisturizers.  I inadvertently purchased a jar without SPF—essentially unusable to me in the summer.

reviews.headline: Allergic reaction!!
reviews.comments: I tried this laat night and my face was getting so itchy within an hour of putting it on. I wiped it off before bed but woke up this morning with a swollen and itchy face. My face is not usually sensitive like this, but if you are sensitive i would definitely not recommend this.

reviews.headline: Severe allergic—anaphylactic—reaction
reviews.comments: I used this cream on and off for many years with no adverse effects. This time, I had a serious allergic reaction that has lasted for a week. My lips got very swollen, and itchy, sore blisters appeared all over my body. Beware if you are sensitive to chemicals.

reviews.headline: Great product but not for sensitive skin
reviews.comments: I loved how soft it made my skin and if you can tolerate it, it's a great product. Love Lancome. However, there is a strong fragrance to it and my sensitive skin got very irritated. I wish they made a fragrance free version, I would repurchase. Until then, I have to give it away

reviews.headline: Irritating
reviews.comments: I hate to say it but this moisturizer burned on my face. It happened 2-3 times because at first I wasn't sure if it was this product or not. It does have a smell to it but I don't find it overpowering. For the few times I used it, it did seem to moisturize well. I'm glad this works for other folks :)

reviews.headline: My girlfriend is trying it.
reviews.comments: My girlfriend is trying it, because this is the wrong one that I bought.  She likes the day cream with 25 SPF. So far no complaints with her using it for a week now. I'm going to buy her the Lancome Aquagel SPF 50 for a base of her make-up and sun protection and see if they work well together. She already uses the Lancome Rose water Lotion and Toner.

reviews.headline: Strong perfume fragrance
reviews.comments: The cream works well but it has a strong fragrance. I have used this cream for about a month and the fragrance is too much for me. I will continue to use it but wish there was a fragrance free version.

reviews.headline: Lancome
reviews.comments: I have used this product for years, it clears my face leaves it smooth and young looking. I recommend this product

reviews.headline: Can't get enough
reviews.comments: I bought the Lancome holiday gift pack with this included. Otherwise I don't think I would've ever bought it. Out of the entire set this is the one I use consistently because of the way it feels. Woke up today and forgot I used to have age spots. They're gone.

reviews.headline: perfume
reviews.comments: This has a strong perfume smell.  I bought it half off during days of beauty.  Reviews are good but that strong perfume smell.  might use it on chest instead of face to use up.

reviews.headline: HPN 300 Peptide Cream
reviews.comments: Ive tried a lot of face creams, this is definitely in my top 3. This cream is ideal for mornings where you want something moisturizing but not too oily. I can also see a difference in brighness and fine lines. I also feel like this cream works with most skin types. I have dry skin and it works well as a day cream.

reviews.headline: LANCOME HAS THE MAGIC!
reviews.comments: About two months ago I received a super sample of this and I was SHOCKED at the difference in my skin within 48 hours. My fine lines were already fading and my skin was taught. At 46 years old I've tried every serum and moisturizer, including high end brands such as Sunday Riley and Drunk Elephant only to be left with little to no results and wasted money. This particular line of Lancome products is expensive and beyond my normal budget but it is worth every penny. I just started using the serum and these products have changed my life. I will always look for the best sales and discounts but if I would pay full price because this moisturizer is magic and now a permanent staple in my skincare routine and I HIGHLY recommend this for all women my age and up in need of help fighting fine lines and wrinkles and skin elasticity.

reviews.headline: Renergie HPN 300
reviews.comments: This product has improved the appearance of my skin without causing any breakouts. I love the texture and it has a pleasant smell to it

reviews.headline: Amazing
reviews.comments: I've always used the old formula for years, but when I was given the travel size when I had purchased a set it came with it and I DID NOT like it. It felt too gelish that I was skeptical in purchasing this size. But I did anyway because Lancôme has been my go to brand for years now. I feel in love, my face felt so smooth and plump on the first try. Loved the way my makeup set and looks. Definitely a keeper!!

reviews.headline: Would purchase again
reviews.comments: Nice product. Could see results in a couple days

reviews.headline: I might buy this again.
reviews.comments: Yes, my skin feels better and there may be some improvement in fine lines. The price is too high for my budget and I am disappointed in the packaging. The outside jar is much bigger than the actual inside pot that holds the product. Seems dishonest.

reviews.headline: So firm !!!
reviews.comments: This cream is magic in a bottle. My skin feels more hydrated, firmed, and my fine lines have minimized. Buying a backup now!!

reviews.headline: smooth
reviews.comments: I can't yet speak to long term results but the immediate results are great so far. cream is light and fully absorbs in about 15 minutes. Skin is left soft smooth and natural not shiny or oily.  skin tone looks evened, pores blurred. lines are plumper and nasolabial folds appear firmed. Thats pretty good for immediate results.

faceoff_positive.comments: Unbelievable!!!!  I'm calling this cream SPANX ON STEROIDS!!!!  Especially effective on my lower jaw line, where everything was starting to head south very quickly!  Amazing results, in just a couple of weeks!!!
faceoff_positive.headline: Results…FAST!

faceoff_negative.comments: Received Rénergie H.P.N. 300-Peptide Cream as a sample and was blown away.  My skin looked amazing with just one application.  So why only 3 stars?  The darn fragrance.  Yes, the fragrance is light, but it is still there.  I am sensitive to fragrance and developed a headache from it. I do not usually spend this much on moisturizer but was strongly considering it due to it's effectiveness.  Why or why does Lancome find the need to add fragrance to skin care products. Skin creams are not meant to service as perfumes.  That is what perfume is for.  Lancome has a whole line of perfumes.  Why introduce skin care products with added fragrance to "fight' with your perfume line???  Please start offering fragrance free skin care.
faceoff_negative.headline: Miracle cream...but cannot use it
